snippet.title: Gore Doctor - Horror Game Reveal Trailer - by Salient Games! Now available!
snippet.description:
Get it now on Steam!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/2495990/Gore_Doctor/

Gore Doctor is an immersive horror game set to unleash spine-chilling thrills on PC. You find yourself in the institute of a tormented doctor who, driven by desperation after losing his wife, descends into madness and becomes convinced that death is the only respite.
